001249r 2               ; Reason -- Verify (Y,A) <= FRETOP, calling Garbag and rechecking on
001249r 2               ; failure.  We omit the msbasic save/restore of TEMP1..FAC-1 because in
001249r 2               ; our layout TEMP1 is above FAC; Garbag only writes to its own ZP scratch
001249r 2               ; (FNCNAM/Z52/HIGHDS/HIGHTR/INDEX/LOWTR/DSCLEN) so callers that have FAC
001249r 2               ; live across Reason must save FAC themselves.  Current callers do.
