0021C2r 2               ; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
0021C2r 2               ; Statement: REM -- skip to end of line.
0021C2r 2               ; Statement: DATA -- treated like REM at execution time (just skip).
0021C2r 2               ; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
0021C2r 2               BasCmdRem:
0021C2r 2  20 rr rr             jsr     BasRemn
