00220Cr 2                       ; Otherwise dispatch as a statement (msbasic: jmp EXECUTE_STATEMENT).
00220Cr 2  4C rr rr             jmp     BasExecuteStatement
00220Fr 2               @goto:
00220Fr 2  4C rr rr             jmp     BasCmdGoto
